4. Graphics tools — NOT bundled, invoked as subprocesses
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Graphics conversion optionally shells out to Ghostscript (`gs`, AGPL-3.0),
MuPDF (`mutool`, AGPL-3.0), Poppler (`pdftocairo`, GPL-2.0), and ImageMagick
(`convert`). These are provided by the user's system, invoked only as separate
processes (never linked), so their copyleft terms do not extend to this binary.
